translated: Kjellgren, Thorsten Henrik, national bank director, Mariestad, born 28/4/82 in Una, Mohilev governorate, Russia, son of Vilhelm K. and Augusta Hebbe. Married 12, with Elsa Sandwall. Children: Anders born 13, Thorsten 16, Gunvor 17, Bengt 20. Completed high school in Jönikiöping 02. Started working in the national bank in 02, acting registrar and bookkeeper in 09, permanent in 10, director at the national bank department office in Mariestad since 36. Chairman of the first special tax committee for Skaraborg County. Certified by the examination board in 44, substitute for the guardian. Knight of the Royal Order of Vasa.
